{
  "episode_id": "2026-06-30",
  "chunks": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "听众朋友大家好，欢迎收听 AI 每日先锋，今天是 2026 年 6 月 30 日。我是晓晓。",
      "start": 1.0,
      "duration": 7.663,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_001_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_001_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "大家好，我是博文。",
      "start": 9.112,
      "duration": 1.829,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_002_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_002_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "哎博文，最近你有没有一种感觉？AI 这个圈子现在像按了快进键，钱往头部涌，技术往落地跑，两边同时在使劲加速。",
      "start": 11.438,
      "duration": 9.839,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_003_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_003_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "嗯，你这个观察很敏锐。资本市场这半年明显在分化，资金越来越向头部聚集。",
      "start": 21.73,
      "duration": 8.533,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_004_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_004_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "对，所以今天咱们就顺着这条线索聊——既有那种不得不烧钱的硬仗，也有真正扎根到产业里的新故事。",
      "start": 30.668,
      "duration": 8.403,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_005_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_005_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "先说最近最受关注的一件事吧。DeepSeek 那边有动静了，我看到有消息说，是 Claude 新出的 Mythos 模型让梁文锋下了决心，要启动一轮重大融资？",
      "start": 39.504,
      "duration": 11.146,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_006_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_006_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "晓晓你关注得挺快。这件事背景确实值得好好拆解一下。",
      "start": 51.115,
      "duration": 4.833,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_007_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_007_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 8,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "你给我讲讲呗，Mythos 这个名字我听着就觉得挺\"玄\"，它到底厉害在哪？",
      "start": 56.41,
      "duration": 5.747,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_008_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_008_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 9,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "你可以这么理解——之前大模型之间的差距，好比是同一所高中的尖子生和普通生的区别，大家底子差不多，只是有的人发挥好一点。",
      "start": 62.608,
      "duration": 10.58,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_009_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_009_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 10,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "嗯嗯。",
      "start": 73.688,
      "duration": 0.697,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_010_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_010_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 11,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "但 Mythos 这一代出来，等于直接换了个赛道的玩家。它在推理深度、长程规划这些维度上，呈现出来的是一种\"代际跃迁\"。",
      "start": 74.823,
      "duration": 11.494,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_011_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_011_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 12,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "哎等等，代际跃迁这个词太学术了，能给我翻译翻译吗？",
      "start": 86.778,
      "duration": 4.615,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_012_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_012_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 13,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "哈哈哈好。简单说就是——以前大家跑步都穿同一款鞋，只是有人跑得快一点；现在突然有人换了双带推进器的，跑法完全不一样了。",
      "start": 91.838,
      "duration": 10.884,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_013_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_013_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 14,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "哦！这个比喻我懂了。那 DeepSeek 看到这种差距，是不是就坐不住了？",
      "start": 103.196,
      "duration": 4.92,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_014_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_014_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 15,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "没错。DeepSeek 之前走的路线是靠算法效率去撬动算力天花板，用更少的卡办更多的事。但 Mythos 这种模型的训练规模，可能已经到了一个临界点。",
      "start": 108.543,
      "duration": 13.671,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_015_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_015_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 16,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "临界点？",
      "start": 122.678,
      "duration": 0.871,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_016_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_016_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 17,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "嗯，就是说光靠\"省着用\"已经不够了，必须在算力储备上拉到同一个量级才能继续竞争。这就不是省吃俭用的问题了，是得真金白银去买米下锅。",
      "start": 123.966,
      "duration": 15.499,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_017_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_017_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 18,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "哇，这个比喻太形象了。所以梁文锋这次融资，本质上是被逼出来的\"生存保卫战\"？",
      "start": 139.901,
      "duration": 6.661,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_018_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_018_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 19,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "你这么说也成立，但其实也是主动选择。DeepSeek 的路线本来就不靠堆算力出名，现在面对这种代际压力，必须拿到足够的\"燃料\"才能保持自己的节奏。",
      "start": 146.979,
      "duration": 13.279,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_019_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_019_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 20,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "那博文，你觉得这轮融资之后，中国大模型格局会怎么走？",
      "start": 160.754,
      "duration": 4.833,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_020_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_020_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 21,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "我觉得会更残酷。说白了就是头部吃肉，腰部喝汤，尾部连汤渣都看不到。",
      "start": 165.999,
      "duration": 6.618,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_021_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_021_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 22,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "哈，你这形容也太扎心了。",
      "start": 173.096,
      "duration": 2.395,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_022_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_022_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 23,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "但是事实。中小实验室如果没有差异化的场景落地能力，这一两年会非常难过。",
      "start": 175.923,
      "duration": 8.229,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_023_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_023_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 24,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "嗯，确实。那这种\"烧钱换生存\"的局面，是不是也意味着中美 AI 竞赛进入了新阶段？",
      "start": 184.62,
      "duration": 7.053,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_024_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_024_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 25,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "没错。之前拼的是论文和 demo，现在拼的是谁能持续烧、烧得久。这已经不是技术赛，是耐力赛了。",
      "start": 192.163,
      "duration": 10.188,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_025_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_025_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 26,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "好家伙，听你这么一说，感觉 DeepSeek 这一轮融资，整个行业的风向标意义比它本身的金额还大。",
      "start": 202.828,
      "duration": 8.054,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_026_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_026_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 27,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "这个观察很到位。融资本身只是结果，但折射出来的是整个中国大模型竞争逻辑的转变。",
      "start": 211.3,
      "duration": 8.577,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_027_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_027_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 28,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "哎博文，说到大模型之后下一个火的方向，你是不是也想到了具身智能？",
      "start": 220.316,
      "duration": 5.312,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_028_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_028_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 29,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "嗯，最近这个词确实热得发烫。",
      "start": 226.04,
      "duration": 2.83,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_029_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_029_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 30,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "对，我看到一个让我挺震撼的消息——大湾区那边出了一个 200 亿估值的具身智能独角兽，叫智平方。国家队、千亿产业资本、头部财投全都入局了。",
      "start": 229.363,
      "duration": 13.235,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_030_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_030_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 31,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "你看到的是智平方那轮融资吧？这家公司我有关注，背景挺有意思。",
      "start": 243.007,
      "duration": 6.226,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_031_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_031_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 32,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "说说说说。",
      "start": 249.72,
      "duration": 1.176,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_032_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_032_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 33,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "它的核心是做通用智能机器人的\"大脑\"，也就是让机器人真正能理解物理世界、能做复杂任务的那一套系统。",
      "start": 251.338,
      "duration": 10.101,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_033_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_033_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_b_professional",
        "lively": "host_b_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 34,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "哦，这个\"大脑\"听着就",
      "start": 261.899,
      "duration": 1.959,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_034_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_034_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 35,
      "host": "A",
      "text": "好了听众朋友们，以上就是今天的AI每日先锋。感谢收听，我们明天见！",
      "start": 264.329,
      "duration": 5.181,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_035_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_035_lively.mp3"
      },
      "voices": {
        "professional": "host_a_professional",
        "lively": "host_a_lively"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 36,
      "host": "B",
      "text": "拜拜！",
      "start": 269.922,
      "duration": 0.871,
      "audios": {
        "professional": "chunk_036_professional.mp3",
        "lively": "chunk_036_lively.mp3"
      },
